<reference id="api_createtextureview">
    <title><ph keyref="CreateTextureView"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc"
            ><?oxy_comment_start author="admin" timestamp="20210812T175336+0800" comment="没有中文文档"?>创建
            TextureView。<?oxy_comment_end?></ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="CreateTextureView"/>
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java">public static TextureView CreateTextureView(Context context) {
    return new TextureView(context);</codeblock>
                <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec"/>
                <codeblock props="windows" outputclass="language-cpp"/>
                <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
                <codeblock props="unity" outputclass="language-csharp"/>
                <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
                <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart"/>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <dl outputclass="deprecated">
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>弃用：</dt>
                    <dd>此方法已废弃。</dd>
                </dlentry>  
            </dl>
            <p>你可以调用该方法创建 TextureView，which is suitable for scenarios that require scaling,
                rotation, and parallel coordinate translation of video images, such as screen
                sharing. The operation and layout of the view are managed by the app, and the Agora
                SDK renders the view provided by the app.</p>
            <p>如果你需要使用 SurfaceView，请调用本方法；如果你需要使用 SurfaceView，请调用 <xref keyref="CreateRendererView"/>
                方法。详见 <xref
                    href="https://source.android.google.cn/devices/graphics/arch-tv#surface_or_texture"
                    format="html" scope="external">TextureView 和 SurfaceView 的区别</xref> 和 <xref
                    href="https://github.com/crosswalk-project/crosswalk-website/wiki/Android-SurfaceView-vs-TextureView"
                    format="html" scope="external">选择 SurfaceView 或 TextureView</xref>。 <note
                    type="attention">请在主线程调用该方法。</note></p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>参数</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>context</pt>
                    <pd>安卓活动 (Android Activity) 的上下文。 </pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values">
            <title>返回值</title>
            <p>TextureView</p>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
